# 本地或私有 Skill 变体和注册表覆盖不进入镜像；受控 registry.yaml 与 SKILL.md 保留
resources/skills/**/*.local.md
resources/skills/**/*.private.md
resources/skills/registry.local.yaml
resources/skills/registry.private.yaml

